@startuml
title Use Case 3: View Music Community Board

actor User
participant WebInterface
participant PostController
database Database

User -> WebInterface: requestCommunityBoard()
activate WebInterface
WebInterface -> PostController: getRecentPosts()
activate PostController
PostController -> Database: fetchPosts(order=recent)
activate Database
Database --> PostController: postList
deactivate Database
PostController --> WebInterface: formattedPosts
deactivate PostController
WebInterface --> User: displayPosts(postList)
deactivate WebInterface

@enduml
